Author: coolcat411
Text: Restricting REALLY fucks up your brain chemistry, so go easy on yourself. Unfortunately, that’s the price you’re going to have to ask yourself if it’s worth to pay.

Author: jazminonacloud
Text: Yep alllll of that, friend. I try doubly hard to just completely fast as I’ve noticed when I’m restricting but still eating here and there my blood sugar is out of whack and makes me act like a lunatic.
